Give it to Pinky.

47:25.722 --> 47:28.191
That's a big bar mitzvah present.

47:28.225 --> 47:30.026
Somebody's got to run that shithole.

47:30.060 --> 47:32.812
Something more important.

47:32.814 --> 47:34.814
We got to set this meeting.

47:34.816 --> 47:37.333
Sooner is better.

47:37.367 --> 47:40.152
Everyone from Pittsburgh to Podunk.

47:40.204 --> 47:42.822
Lay out the rules before
people get their own ideas.

47:42.873 --> 47:45.124
Now, I can make these phone calls.

47:45.158 --> 47:47.326
That'll be the easiest.

47:47.361 --> 47:51.714
Most of these guys, we all
cut our teeth on Mulberry Bend.

47:51.748 --> 47:53.249
So when they hear it from me...

47:53.300 --> 47:55.218
We're gonna handle it, Johnny.

47:57.638 --> 48:00.256
These are big changes.

48:00.307 --> 48:02.341
I want to be sure everything goes...

48:02.392 --> 48:05.511
We appreciate all your advice.

48:05.546 --> 48:07.763
Couldn't have done it without you.

48:08.849 --> 48:11.901
Jesus, look at you alter kockers.

48:11.935 --> 48:13.819
We celebrating or not?

48:18.659 --> 48:20.776
This could be a good year, Charlie.

48:20.827 --> 48:22.194
So what are you waiting for?

48:22.246 --> 48:24.080
Let's pop those bottles already.

48:24.114 --> 48:26.365
Let's get this thing going.

48:27.367 --> 48:29.752
Whoo!

48:29.786 --> 48:31.120
Ha ha!

48:31.171 --> 48:32.838
Whoo!

48:34.007 --> 48:36.175
Here you go. Let's cut a rug.

48:40.048 --> 48:41.797
Who is it?

48:41.848 --> 48:44.050
Joe Harper.

48:44.968 --> 48:47.053
It's unlocked.

48:55.112 --> 48:58.531
Thought you might want
it cleaned up in here.

48:58.565 --> 49:00.700
Not right now.

49:04.905 --> 49:07.573
You want refills on those?

49:08.825 --> 49:11.210
Just clear the empties.

49:14.081 --> 49:15.798
All the booze, out.

49:29.146 --> 49:31.314
Do you know what happened?

49:35.502 --> 49:36.869
You won.

49:36.903 --> 49:40.272
Mickey, Arquimedes,

49:40.274 --> 49:42.108
they're not coming back.

49:42.142 --> 49:43.776
Understand?

49:45.412 --> 49:48.748
What's it like when you see it?

49:51.251 --> 49:53.319
You tell yourself it's quick.

49:53.353 --> 49:56.122
But you don't know.

49:56.124 --> 49:59.792
You can't know until it's you.

49:59.843 --> 50:02.128
And then you'll never tell anyone.

50:04.715 --> 50:07.383
Is the club staying open?

50:09.136 --> 50:11.604
Ask the new boss.

50:14.808 --> 50:17.476
You know, there's things I can do for you.

50:19.479 --> 50:21.197
Sure.

50:21.231 --> 50:23.549
You can sweep the sand.

50:23.583 --> 50:25.201
