50:44.838 --> 50:46.305
Sir?

50:47.758 --> 50:49.408
Just take the money.

50:50.727 --> 50:52.344
Take it.

50:55.098 --> 50:57.683
Then do whatever you want, you stupid hick.

50:57.734 --> 50:59.602
But do us both a favor

50:59.653 --> 51:02.455
and get the fuck away from me.

51:58.829 --> 52:00.546
I'm sorry.

52:00.580 --> 52:03.215
Business took longer than I expected.

52:06.119 --> 52:08.554
It's my job.

52:08.588 --> 52:11.640
I don't have a choice. You know that.

52:13.844 --> 52:15.845
