52:15.896 --> 52:17.680
What did you say to her?

52:17.714 --> 52:19.165
What?

52:19.199 --> 52:20.649
What did you say?

52:20.684 --> 52:23.569
- Nothing. What...
- She's run off.

52:23.603 --> 52:24.987
When?

52:25.021 --> 52:26.438
I was asleep.

52:26.490 --> 52:28.657
She take anything?

52:28.692 --> 52:30.476
- I don't know.
- Did you look?

52:30.510 --> 52:32.278
Why would you even ask me that?

52:32.280 --> 52:34.163
Because she's a thief.

52:34.197 --> 52:36.415
She is a thief. That's what she is.

52:36.449 --> 52:38.284
She was someone who needed help.

52:38.335 --> 52:41.787
I tried. I tried.

52:43.256 --> 52:44.957
I care about you.

52:44.959 --> 52:47.459
I care about the family
we're going to have together.

52:47.511 --> 52:49.195
That's all that matters to me.

52:49.229 --> 52:51.463
You can't fix everything.

52:53.467 --> 52:56.435
Come back.

52:56.469 --> 52:58.554
Please come back.

53:02.526 --> 53:05.611
