53:30.420 --> 53:33.138
"Dear Sheriff Enoch.

53:33.173 --> 53:36.058
You came to my aid once

53:36.092 --> 53:39.144
a very long time ago.

53:39.179 --> 53:42.181
I write in the last
hope that you can find it

53:42.232 --> 53:45.484
